    "abstract": "<jats:p>Vellore Arthi of University of California, Irvine, reviews \u201cControlling Contagion: Epidemics and Institutions from the Black Death to Covid\u201d by Sheilagh Ogilvie. The Econlit abstract of this book begins: \u201cExplores the past seven centuries of history to investigate how human societies dealt with epidemic disease, highlighting the features that have made institutional frameworks better at coordinating responses to epidemics and better at devising innovations to improve societal learning.\u201d</jats:p>",
